###  RegisterHandler

NetworkServer  NetworkClient  `RegisterHandler(short msgType, Networking.NetworkMessageDelegate handler);` 


*  msgType  short Unity  [MsgType](http://docs.unity3d.com/ScriptReference/Networking.MsgType.html) 
~~
*  handler  NetworkMessageDelegate  __delegate void NetworkMessageDelegate( Networking.NetworkMessage netMsg )__
 C#  delegate, 


